Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Summer's end, September 1985
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xmrs
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 Sep 1985
End of summer sees the holiday cottages empty and normal life resume in the coastal towns. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less